# Design Tokens — [Project Name]

> Single source of truth for all visual decisions. Claude must use these tokens — never invent values.

## Colors

### Brand
| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `color.primary` | [#hex] | Primary actions, links |
| `color.primary.hover` | [#hex] | Primary hover state |
| `color.secondary` | [#hex] | Secondary actions |

### Semantic
| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `color.success` | [#hex] | Success states, confirmations |
| `color.warning` | [#hex] | Warning states, caution |
| `color.error` | [#hex] | Error states, destructive actions |
| `color.info` | [#hex] | Informational states |

### Neutral
| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `color.text.primary` | [#hex] | Body text, headings |
| `color.text.secondary` | [#hex] | Captions, labels |
| `color.text.disabled` | [#hex] | Disabled text |
| `color.bg.page` | [#hex] | Page background |
| `color.bg.surface` | [#hex] | Card/panel background |
| `color.bg.overlay` | [rgba] | Modal overlay |
| `color.border` | [#hex] | Default borders |

